metadata.name: Fat Baby Bat #1/1
metadata.description:
One day, Fat Baby Bat saw the Little Joker licking candy. And he started to follow, jumping off the rooftops. When the Little Joker entered a dark alley, the fat baby bat took Little Joker's candy and ran away. Because the sugar fat belly was his biggest weakness.

Artwork by **Erdogan Paksoy**.
